# ============================================================
# Operational summary (one line for downstream PLAN.bn use)
# ============================================================
#
# Cheapcode's product proposition reduces to a single thermodynamic
# objective with substrate-invariant backing: every dollar a user pays
# for an answer they don't get is T_0·ΔS_gen, and the smarter-faster-
# cheaper pitch literally minimizes that quantity. The five waste
# sources of F7 are the measurable handles. Atom 0018 is the runtime
# procedure. Caching, falsification, and routing-discipline are the
# three thermodynamically-required levers (F8 a/b/c).
#
# Falsifier for F29 as a whole: if a 2026 production agent stack
# demonstrably achieves Pareto-better $/correct_output by IGNORING
# any of the five waste sources of F7, the decomposition is
# incomplete and F29 needs revision. This has not been observed in
# any cheapcode benchmark to date.
